Commentary Text: J Suchith to Pant, out Prithvi Shaw Run Out!! Oh dear! Chaos everywhere. Pant skips down and is beaten by the in-spin. Bairstow fails to collect it cleanly and the DC skipper survives a stumping chance. But there's more drama. Prithvi Shaw wanders out of his crease and is halfway down. By the time he can turn around and make his ground, the throw comes to the bowler's end from short fine leg. Suchith quickly whipped off the bails to catch Shaw short of his crease. A good knock comes to a premature end. Prithvi Shaw run out (Khaleel Ahmed/J Suchith) 53(39) [4s-7 6s-1]
